Swazi lawmakers are demanding that
Prime Minister Barnabas Sibusiso Dlamini and his cabinet resign
following the publication of a report into the purchase of land,
according to the Parliament Select Committee Land Probe Report
tabled in Parliament yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
